":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T08:05:30.000Z","msg":"頭先望左下 #1314, 先唔計佢租鋪單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n翠華2012年招股書 以&ldquo;收益&rdquo;做分母 同2018年做比較<br />\n毛利都大約維持70%, not bad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但員工成本 由25%升到28%<br />\n折舊3% -&gt; 5%<br />\n租金13% -&gt; 18%<br />\n其他營運開支6% -&gt; 9%<br />\n最後純利率(唔計JV)<br />\n13% -&gt; 2%<br />\n<br />\n睇返 太興，2016 2017 2018<br />\n毛率大約71% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> not bad<br />\n但純利得7-9%<br />\n翠華本身有13%都跌到2%<br />\n自己諗下餐飲做唔做得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"餐飲NPM低好正常，翠華上市嗰陣話有13%擺到明執到靚仔晒先上架啦。<br />\n<br />\n太興7-9%都肯定有執過，真係買，都只係炒一轉算啦，長線瓜梗架"},{"pid":"45343e7f4bd5e54ee9470ea7b8bb7433aaf18391","tid":1175880,"uid":251552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:56:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b2d246bc315f3ba67e90f6fa0b411d1b07b116b","tid":1175880,"uid":246729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"46e9f4e33fc0cafa13e98f5acdce39c34e753c66","tid":1175880,"uid":150989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61fbfa332efe828758a6dea3471a9d69d411ccef","tid":1175880,"uid":246729,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"嘉濤 老人院 好似幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"原因？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"賺錢能力,純利率大約22%, 上市前ROA~40%<br />\n由於佢高負債, ROE做到86%<br />\n上市前8間院, 千幾個床位<br />\n上市集資額等於佢依家嘅總資產,<br />\n計劃往後會整多6間, 再多接近一千個床<br />\n佢床位收位無松齡咁高, 但Profit ratio高好多<br />\n<br />\n依家政府懶得自己搞老人院, 只會出錢買私人位做補貼<br />\n有一半收入係來自社福署<br />\n暫時睇到咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfcde88fdaceb46f36d319b